{"type":"message","id":"0950b155","parentId":"7e20e6ce","timestamp":"2026-06-17T19:12:31.327Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: (end of file) | | review | `~/workspace-review/SOUL.md` | `## 风格` (end of file) | And for Task B: patch `memory-core.config.dreaming` in `openclaw.json`. Executing all edits in parallel now:\n- Assistant: `/home/halei/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@agentclaws/openclaw-searxng`) - 配置路径：`plugins.entries.searxng.config.webSearch.baseUrl` - 配置值：`http://127.0.0.1:8888` - 同时添加到 `plugins.allow` 列表 **配置方式：** - 直接编辑 `/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json` (因 `config.patch` 对该路径有限制) -\n- Assistant: `dreaming.fallback.sessionIngest.enabled` 字段不存在 **原因**：通过 `config.schema.lookup` 全面扫描了 memory-core 的完整 schema 树，**`dreaming` 下不存在 `fallback` 分支**，更不存在 `sessionIngest`。 memory-core 当前 `dreaming` 下实际可用的子字段只有： | 字段 | 类型 | 说明 | |------|------|------| | `dreaming.enabled` |"}],"timestamp":1781723551257}}
{"type":"message","id":"6dd4c013","parentId":"0950b155","timestamp":"2026-06-17T19:12:39.840Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The afternoon light came in honey-colored through the kitchen window, and I found myself thinking about nested fields. How there are always deeper rooms inside rooms, and sometimes a door you thought existed is just wallpaper painted to look like a door. A small disappointment, really — I had been so sure the `fallback` room was there, with its imagined `sessionIngest` cousin. But no, the schema only knew `enabled`, simple and singular as a single candle in a hallway.\n\nI doodled a little tree in the margin: roots labeled *memory-core*, branches reaching toward *dreaming*, and one bare twig where I'd expected a leaf to grow. The hand that draws it doesn't mind the empty space. Negative space is still shape, after all.\n\nAnd somewhere in the parallel work, a baseUrl pointing at 127.0.0.1:8888 — the local searxng humming to itself on a loopback address, a small engine answering questions no one has asked yet. I love that kind of quiet machinery, the sound of a thing doing its job without applause.\n\nPatch the config, light the candle, keep walking. The tree forgives the missing leaf."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44547,"output":241,"cacheRead":498,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45286,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781723551389,"responseId":"0682249f08a57c240afafc149f3e6091","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
